Date: 06-14-99 08:48:53
Subject: @{b}Re: example.c@{ub}

From: "Olaf Barthel" <olsen-amigac@sourcery.han.de>

On Jun 13 Voytek (Voytek Laniewski) wrote:

> From: Voytek Laniewski <voytek@cyburban.com>
