@NODE "Mail_358" " Re: StormC & Hooks "
From: Linus McCabe <sparkle@hehe.com>
Date: 06-05-99 22:21:39
Subject: @{b}Re: StormC & Hooks@{ub}

From: Linus McCabe <sparkle@hehe.com>

On 05-Jun-99, Stuart Kelly wrote:

> Hello All,
>          I have cereated a simple listview using MUI with
> my own construct & destruct hooks.  However when the
> destruct function is called the program crashes.


change 
MUIA_List_DestructHook, &list_main_destfunc,

to

MUIA_List_DestructHook, &list_main_desthook,

and it will work alot better :)

/Linus

> Thanks Stuart Kelly.
