Subject: @{b}Re: StormC & Hooks@{ub}

From: Stuart Kelly <amigac@dkelly1.demon.co.uk>

Hello Yves & Linus,

> 1) As far as I see there's no need to use SAVEDS and ASM
> macros in StromC, because they are not supported.
StromC does support __saveds but not ASM.

Thanks Linus for the answer - it was a simple typing mistake
that I missed. I'll correct it and try again.

Thanks Stuart Kelly.


