@NODE "Mail_378" " Re: Text file lines "
From: Allan Odgaard <Duff@DIKU.DK>
Date: 06-23-99 03:24:51
Subject: @{b}Re: Text file lines@{ub}

From: Allan Odgaard <Duff@DIKU.DK>

On 23-Jun-99, Mike Carter wrote:

> What do people suggest to be the easiest way to read a line of text
> (upto the NEWLINE \n character) [...]
> FGets includes the NEWLINE so is not good [...]

Since you probably have no way of predicting the next character in the stream
then there's no way around reading the newline ;-) It's definitely more
efficient to use FGets rather than FGetc in a loop.

Regards Allan
